{"id":495901,"date":"2025-03-13T10:33:43","date_gmt":"2025-03-13T14:33:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/?p=495901"},"modified":"2025-03-13T10:33:47","modified_gmt":"2025-03-13T14:33:47","slug":"piers-morgan-says-hes-heard-alarming-things-about-kate-middleton-amid-princess-of-wales-continued-absence","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2025\/03\/piers-morgan-says-hes-heard-alarming-things-about-kate-middleton-amid-princess-of-wales-continued-absence\/","title":{"rendered":"Piers Morgan Says He&#8217;s Heard &#8216;Alarming Things&#8217; About Kate &hellip;"},"content":{"rendered":"<span class=\"span-reading-time rt-reading-time\" style=\"display: block;\"><span class=\"rt-label rt-prefix\">Reading Time: <\/span> <span class=\"rt-time\"> 4<\/span> <span class=\"rt-label rt-postfix\">minutes<\/span><\/span>\n<p>Generally, when Piers Morgan comments on royal matters, he takes the side of King Charles, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/stars\/prince-william\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Prince William<\/a>, and Kate Middleton.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So it came as a surprise when Morgan discussed <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/03\/john-oliver-thinks-kate-middleton-might-be-dead\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kate&rsquo;s absence<\/a> from royal life and shared his belief that palace officials were hiding something.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Addressing the matter on his talk show <em>Uncensored<\/em> last year, Morgan revealed that he had heard &ldquo;alarming things&rdquo; about the Princess of Wales.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Catherine, Princess Of Wales is seen during the opening of Evelina London's new children's day surgery unit on December 5, 2023 in London, England. \" class=\"wp-image-495902\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-735x490.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-335x223.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-347x231.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-520x347.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-640x427.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-960x640.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1080x720.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Catherine, Princess Of Wales is seen during the opening of Evelina London's new children's day surgery unit on December 5, 2023 in London, England. \" class=\"wp-image-495902 eager-load\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-735x490.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-335x223.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-347x231.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-520x347.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-640x427.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-960x640.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-1080x720.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1825444049-scaled.jpg\" data-no-svg=\"1\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Catherine, Princess Of Wales is seen during the opening of Evelina London&rsquo;s new children&rsquo;s day surgery unit on December 5, 2023 in London, England. <span class=\"image-caption-credit\"> (Photo by Ian Vogler &ndash; WPA Pool\/Getty Images)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>He also criticized the palace&rsquo;s attempts to undermine widespread conspiracy theories via misleading comments and doctored photos.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In a moment that was shockingly out of step with his usual stance on the royals, Morgan admitted that the king and company &ldquo;got it wrong,&rdquo; adding that &ldquo;the palace could be hiding something.&rdquo;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This was before we knew that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/09\/prince-william-kate-middleton-cancer-battle-update\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kate was battling cancer<\/a> and had stepped away from the spotlight in order to undergo treatment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When we learned of her condition, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/06\/piers-morgan-kate-middleton-cancer-diagnosis\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Piers demanded that Kate disclose every detail<\/a>. Thankfully, she has insisted on her right to privacy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/09\/kate-middleton-officially-returns-to-work-following-cancer-battle\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kate has since returned<\/a> to full-time royal duty. But Piers has yet to apologize for speculating wildly and propagating conspiracy theories.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-piers-morgan-speaks-out-on-kate-middleton-controversy\">Piers Morgan Speaks Out on Kate Middleton Controversy<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-683x1024.jpg\" alt='Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The \"Together At Christmas\" Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.' class=\"wp-image-495905\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-1366x2048.jpg 1366w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-735x1102.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-223x335.jpg 223w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-231x347.jpg 231w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-347x520.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-427x640.jpg 427w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-640x960.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-683x1024.jpg\" alt='Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The \"Together At Christmas\" Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.' class=\"wp-image-495905 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-1366x2048.jpg 1366w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-735x1102.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-223x335.jpg 223w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-231x347.jpg 231w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-347x520.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-427x640.jpg 427w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-640x960.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840428553-scaled.jpg\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The &ldquo;Together At Christmas&rdquo; Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.<span class=\"image-caption-credit\"> (Photo by Chris Jackson\/Getty Images)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;&lsquo;I&rsquo;ve been told some stuff that, if even half of it is true, it&rsquo;s pretty alarming what is happening,&rdquo; Morgan told his audience (via <em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.independent.co.uk\/life-style\/royal-family\/piers-morgan-kate-middleton-royal-family-b2514240.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Independent<\/a><\/em>) in March 2024, adding:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know what to believe, nor do any of us &mdash; we&rsquo;re not there.&rdquo;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Morgan tempered his comments at the time with a reminder that no one outside of the royal family really knew what was going on with Kate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A week after his remarks, however, the world was clued in by the Princess herself that she was <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/03\/kate-middleton-cancer-health-update\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">battling cancer<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before her announcement, Morgan expressed similar concerns in his column for the <em><a href=\"https:\/\/nypost.com\/2024\/03\/11\/opinion\/kate-middletons-fake-photo-fiasco-proves-the-secretive-royals-must-come-clean\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">New York Post<\/a><\/em>, arguing that the royals&rsquo; culture of silence has no place in the age of information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;The mantra of Britain&rsquo;s greatest monarch, the late, great Queen Elizabeth II, was very simple: Never complain, never explain, and rarely be heard speaking in public,&rdquo; Morgan wrote.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1024x683.jpg\" alt='Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The \"Together At Christmas\" Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.' class=\"wp-image-495906\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-735x490.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-335x223.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-347x231.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-520x347.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-640x427.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-960x640.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1080x720.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1024x683.jpg\" alt='Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The \"Together At Christmas\" Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.' class=\"wp-image-495906 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-735x490.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-335x223.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-347x231.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-520x347.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-640x427.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-960x640.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-1080x720.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1840560983-scaled.jpg\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Catherine, Princess of Wales attends The &ldquo;Together At Christmas&rdquo; Carol Service at Westminster Abbey on December 08, 2023 in London, England.<span class=\"image-caption-credit\"> (Photo by Chris Jackson\/Getty Images)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-piers-morgan-on-the-conspiracy-theories\">Piers Morgan On The Conspiracy Theories<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>He went on to criticize the royals for releasing the now infamous <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/03\/kate-middleton-family-portrait-removed-by-news-agencies-due-to-alleged-editing-wth-is-going-on\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">edited photo of Kate<\/a> in an effort to suppress the rising tide of rumors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;But the conspiracy theories about Kate Middleton&rsquo;s secret health crisis and disappearance from public life, made worse by the manipulated family photo she posted yesterday, when added to the unsettling confusion over what cancer King Charles is suffering from and how serious his condition is, have shown that the old palace way of handling the media has become increasingly obsolete and unworkable,&rdquo; Morgan wrote, adding:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;I feel very sorry for Kate that she&rsquo;s had to go through whatever health issue she&rsquo;s had, which has kept her away from public gaze, and duty, for so long.&rdquo;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Morgan concluded with the following word of caution:<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"686\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-1024x686.jpg\" alt=\"Catherine, Princess Of Wales attends the opening of Evelina London's new children's day surgery unit on December 05, 2023 in London, England.\" class=\"wp-image-495903\" srcset