3746-1536x1029.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-2048x1372.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-735x493.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-335x224.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-347x233.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-520x348.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-640x429.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-960x643.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-1080x724.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/03\/GettyImages-1832703746-scaled.jpg\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Catherine, Princess Of Wales attends the opening of Evelina London&rsquo;s new children&rsquo;s day surgery unit on December 05, 2023 in London, England.<span class=\"image-caption-credit\"> (Photo by Chris Jackson\/Getty Images)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>&ldquo;But my sympathy will erode if it turns out that she and the palace have deliberately misled the media and public about when the photo was taken to convey a false impression about her condition.&rdquo;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-the-latest-with-kate\">The Latest With Kate<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There&rsquo;s still much that we don&rsquo;t know about Kate&rsquo;s cancer and condition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But the good news is that the worst appears to be over.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/202